7019   // We know that there is no self-wrap. Let's take Start and End values and
7020   // look at all intermediate values V1, V2, ..., Vn that IndVar takes during
7021   // the iteration. They either lie inside the range [Min(Start, End),
7022   // Max(Start, End)] or outside it:
